data.description: Welcome Home To Country Living At Its Finest! 16 Prime Acres in Van Zandt County with a Cute Farmhouse. Every inch is used for a great floor plan. Large rooms, Neutral colors through-out. Engineered Hardwood Floors, Decorative Tile in Kitchen, Fresh New Paint Inside and Out, New Gutters, New HVAC in 2020 and a New Roof! Beautiful Hardwood Land and AG Exempt! Zipline and Tree Swing Conveys! Awesome location, close to I20 for commuters. Canton ISD! Schedule A Showing Today! This Will Not Last Long!
